data.description: ~ $5,000 seller concessions towards buyer's mortgage interest rate buydown or buyer's closing costs with an accepted offer! ~ Welcome to Sierra Catalina Estates - prestigious gated community in heart of the beautiful Catalina Foothills and within desirable Catalina Foothills School District! This fabulous, well-maintained and updated residence has it all! It is nestled on a premium cul-de-sac lot with some of the best mountain, city and valley views Tucson has to offer. The house greets you with soaring ceilings, travertine tile (natural stone) floors, stunning see-through gas fireplace, neutral color palette and abundance of natural light. Gourmet kitchen boasts ample cherry cabinetry, granite countertops, complementary tile backsplash, pendant lighting, new high-end slate appliances and an island perfect for entertaining. Spacious master suite includes double custom closets, jetted tub, shower and breathtaking Santa Catalina Mountains vistas. Split floor plan offers lots of privacy for the most discriminating owners. Secondary bedroom has a private balcony access with mountain, valley and city views. One of the guest bedrooms is on the first floor and so is the beautifully updated hall bathroom with walk-in shower. Two car garage with finished epoxy flooring awaits your vehicles. Private backyard is beautifully landscaped with covered patio, extended seating area and mountain view. Newer hot tub with water feature and LED lighting is the cherry on top. Updates and upgrades everywhere you go - new fingerprint resistant slate kitchen appliances (2023), new dryer (2023), newer washer (2022), new water heater (2023), several newer windows, shutters and glass sliding doors, and so on. Don't miss the full list of home improvements available in the Documents section of the listing. The beautifully maintained, gated community has a large pool, spa and direct access to Orange Grove Middle School in one of the very best school districts in Southern Arizona. Less than 1 mile from La Encantada Shopping Center. Welcome home!
